   393→<!-- THE WEEK -->
   394→<section class="week-section">
   395→  <div class="container">
   396→    <div class="section-label fade-up">The week</div>
   397→    <h2 class="section-title fade-up">Seven days, structured to ship.</h2>
   398→    <p class="section-sub fade-up">Each day has a clear theme. You're building the whole time — but we make sure you're building the right things in the right order.</p>
   399→
   400→    <div class="week-grid">
   401→      <div class="day-card fade-up">
   402→        <div class="day-label">Day 1</div>
   403→        <h3>Arrivals + alignment</h3>
   404→        <p>Move in, meet your cohort, set your week goal. What does success look like by Friday? Get brutally honest about where you are.</p>
   405→      </div>
   406→      <div class="day-card fade-up">
   407→        <div class="day-label">Day 2</div>
   408→        <h3>Customer conversations</h3>
   409→        <p>Your first full day is not building. It's talking to users. Structured interviews, real insights, kill your assumptions early.</p>
   410→      </div>
   411→      <div class="day-card fade-up">
   412→        <div class="day-label">Day 3 — 4</div>
   413→        <h3>Deep build</h3>
   414→        <p>Two full days of heads-down work. Morning standups with your mentor. Afternoon unblocking sessions. Evening reviews with the cohort.</p>
   415→      </div>
   416→      <div class="day-card fade-up">
   417→        <div class="day-label">Day 5</div>
   418→        <h3>Test &amp; iterate</h3>
   419→        <p>Get real users on your product. Run experiments. Fix what's broken. Stop adding features. Make what you have work better.</p>
   420→      </div>
   421→      <div class="day-card fade-up">
   422→        <div class="day-label">Day 6</div>
   423→        <h3>Story + pitch prep</h3>
   424→        <p>What's your narrative? Why this, why now, why you? Practice your demo until the story is effortless.</p>
   425→      </div>
   426→      <div class="day-card fade-up">
   427→        <div class="day-label">Day 7</div>
   428→        <h3>Demo Day</h3>
   429→        <p>Investors, mentors, and the broader Habitat community. 10-minute demo + Q&A. The beginning of the next chapter.</p>
   430→      </div>
   431→    </div>
   432→  </div>
   433→</section>
