   435→<!-- MENTORSHIP -->
   436→<section>
   437→  <div class="container">
   438→    <div class="section-label fade-up">Support structure</div>
   439→    <h2 class="section-title fade-up">Not advice. Presence.</h2>
   440→    <p class="section-sub fade-up">The difference between a good program and a transformative one is whether the people helping you are actually in the room.</p>
   441→
   442→    <div class="mentorship-grid">
   443→      <div class="mentorship-card fade-up">
   444→        <h3>Dedicated mentor</h3>
   445→        <p>One practitioner — a founder, operator, or investor who has done what you're trying to do — works with your cohort the full week. Not for 2 hours. For the week.</p>
   446→      </div>
   447→      <div class="mentorship-card fade-up">
   448→        <h3>VC office hours</h3>
   449→        <p>Investors from our network drop in for sessions throughout the week. Not to evaluate you — to help you think clearer. Evaluation happens at Demo Day, not before.</p>
   450→      </div>
   451→      <div class="mentorship-card fade-up">
   452→        <h3>Peer cohort</h3>
   453→        <p>Four other founders at the same stage, with complementary skills, working alongside you. The cohort is small enough to build genuine trust — and honest enough to tell you hard truths.</p>
   454→      </div>
   455→    </div>
   456→  </div>
   457→</section>
