   519→<!-- DEMO DAY -->
   520→<section>
   521→  <div class="container">
   522→    <div class="section-label fade-up">The culmination</div>
   523→    <h2 class="section-title fade-up">Demo Day.</h2>
   524→    <p class="section-sub fade-up">Day seven isn't a formality. It's the moment your week of work meets the people who can help you go further.</p>
   525→
   526→    <div class="demo-day-content">
   527→      <div class="demo-day-left fade-up">
   528→        <p>Demo Day is a curated event open to investors from our network, the broader Habitat community, and select guests. Each founder has 10 minutes: a live product demo, not slides.</p>
   529→        <p>Q&A follows. The conversation continues at the networking session after. Some founders leave with term sheets. Most leave with introductions, feedback, and a clearer path.</p>
   530→        <p>All of them leave knowing exactly what the next 90 days look like.</p>
