   329→<!-- FORMAT -->
   330→<section class="format-section" id="format">
   331→  <div class="container">
   332→    <div class="section-label fade-up">The format</div>
   333→    <h2 class="section-title fade-up">10 hours of focused building.</h2>
   334→    <p class="section-sub fade-up">No slides. No pitch decks at the start. You arrive, you form a team, you build. At the end, you demo a working product to the investors in the room.</p>
   335→
   336→    <div class="timeline fade-up">
   337→      <div class="timeline-item">
   338→        <div class="timeline-time">10:00</div>
   339→        <div class="timeline-dot"><div class="timeline-dot-circle"></div><div class="timeline-dot-line"></div></div>
   340→        <div class="timeline-content">
   341→          <h3>Kickoff &amp; theme reveal</h3>
   342→          <p>The technical theme or problem space is announced. Team up, pick your angle, define your scope. You have 30 minutes to align — then you build.</p>
   343→        </div>
   344→      </div>
   345→      <div class="timeline-item">
   346→        <div class="timeline-time">10:30</div>
   347→        <div class="timeline-dot"><div class="timeline-dot-circle"></div><div class="timeline-dot-line"></div></div>
   348→        <div class="timeline-content">
   349→          <h3>Building begins</h3>
   350→          <p>Heads down. Real code, real infrastructure, real product. Mentors from our sponsor network are in the room to unblock you when you're stuck.</p>
   351→        </div>
   352→      </div>
   353→      <div class="timeline-item">
   354→        <div class="timeline-time">13:00</div>
   355→        <div class="timeline-dot"><div class="timeline-dot-circle"></div><div class="timeline-dot-line"></div></div>
   356→        <div class="timeline-content">
   357→          <h3>Lunch + mid-day check-in</h3>
   358→          <p>Break, eat, recalibrate. Optional 5-minute mid-day check-ins with a mentor if you've hit a wall or want to pressure-test your approach.</p>
   359→        </div>
   360→      </div>
   361→      <div class="timeline-item">
   362→        <div class="timeline-time">14:00</div>
   363→        <div class="timeline-dot"><div class="timeline-dot-circle"></div><div class="timeline-dot-line"></div></div>
   364→        <div class="timeline-content">
   365→          <h3>Back to building</h3>
   366→          <p>Afternoon block. Focus on making it work end-to-end, not just look good. A working demo matters more than a polished UI.</p>
   367→        </div>
   368→      </div>
   369→      <div class="timeline-item">
   370→        <div class="timeline-time">18:00</div>
   371→        <div class="timeline-dot"><div class="timeline-dot-circle"></div><div class="timeline-dot-line"></div></div>
   372→        <div class="timeline-content">
   373→          <h3>Freeze + prep demos</h3>
