   375→        </div>
   376→      </div>
   377→      <div class="timeline-item">
   378→        <div class="timeline-time">19:00</div>
   379→        <div class="timeline-dot"><div class="timeline-dot-circle"></div><div class="timeline-dot-line"></div></div>
   380→        <div class="timeline-content">
   381→          <h3>Demo + investor pitches</h3>
   382→          <p>Each team gets 5 minutes. Live demo, one slide max. Sponsors ask real questions. The best teams get follow-up conversations, not just a prize.</p>
   383→        </div>
   384→      </div>
   385→      <div class="timeline-item">
   386→        <div class="timeline-time">20:00</div>
   387→        <div class="timeline-dot"><div class="timeline-dot-circle"></div><div class="timeline-dot-line"></div></div>
   388→        <div class="timeline-content">
   389→          <h3>Awards + networking</h3>
   390→          <p>Prizes, credits, and introductions. More importantly: the people in this room are who you want to know.</p>
   391→        </div>
   392→      </div>
